rld/~3/T-iwKpFUJKY/index.html</link><description>Saudi Arabia is asking pilgrims to cover their mouths with a mask while in crowded places -- or risk spreading a deadly disease.&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_world/~4/T-iwKpFUJKY" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2013 08:28:46 EDT</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/13/world/meast/saudi-arabia-pilgrims-masks/index.html</feedburner:origLink></item>\r\n<item><title>Police hurt in Belfast riots</title><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/13/world/europe/northern-ireland-unrest/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_world/~3/GyW0s1s-tOg/index.html</link><description>Hundreds of additional police officers are being sent from Britain to Northern Ireland on Saturday after a night of loyalist rioting in Belfast left 32 officers injured across the city, police said.&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_world/~4/GyW0s1s-tOg" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2013 11:18:50 EDT</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/13/world/europe/northern-ireland-unrest/index.html</feedburner:origLink></item>\r\n<item><title>DSK: I have no problem with women</title><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/10/world/europe/france-dsk/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_world/~3/c4i_HQXvGUY/index.html</link><description>Despite his brushes with the law involving allegations of sexual assault and prostitution, Dominique Strauss-Kahn insisted in a CNN interview that he doesn''t "have any kind of problem with women."&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_world/~4/c4i_HQXvGUY" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2013 10:04:56 EDT</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/10/world/europe/france-dsk/index.html</feedburner:origLink></item>\r\n<item><title>Pope lays down law on child abuse</title><gui