69/l/0L0Sreuters0N0Carticle0C20A130C0A70C150Cus0Eusa0Esecurity0Esnowden0EidUSBRE96E0AJC20A130A7150DfeedType0FRSS0GfeedName0FworldNews/story01.htm</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>France confirms body found in Mali is French hostage</title><link>http://feeds.reuters.com/~r/Reuters/worldNews/~3/mtBUHCTHTzg/story01.htm</link><description>PARIS (Reuters) - France confirmed on Monday that a body found in northern Mali was that of the French geologist Philippe Verdon, taken hostage in November 2011.&lt;img width=''1'' height=''1'' src=''http://reuters.us.feedsportal.com/c/35217/f/654198/s/2eb1de18/mf.gif'' border=''0''/&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;\r\n&lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=mtBUHCTHTzg:hrfX967waek:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=mtBUHCTHTzg:hrfX967waek:F7zBnMyn0Lo"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?i=mtBUHCTHTzg:hrfX967waek:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=mtBUHCTHTzg:hrfX967waek:V_sGLiPBpWU"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?i=mtBUHCTHTzg:hrfX967waek:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Reuters/worldNews/~4/mtBUHCTHTzg" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><category domain="">worldNews</category><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2013 19:25:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/07/15/us-france-hostage-mali-idUSBRE96E0RW20130715?feedType=RSS&amp;feedName=worldNews</guid><feedburner:origLink>http://reuters.us.feedsportal.com/c/35217/f/654198/s/2eb1de18/l/0L0Sreuters0N0Carticle0C20A130C0A70C150Cus0Efrance0Ehostage0Emali0EidUSBRE96E0ARW20A130A7150DfeedType0FRSS0GfeedName0FworldNews/story01.htm</feedburner:origLink></item><item><tit