 domain="">worldNews</category><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2013 18:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/07/15/us-egypt-protests-usa-aid-idUSBRE96E0SC20130715?feedType=RSS&amp;feedName=worldNews</guid><feedburner:origLink>http://reuters.us.feedsportal.com/c/35217/f/654198/s/2eb1c190/l/0L0Sreuters0N0Carticle0C20A130C0A70C150Cus0Eegypt0Eprotests0Eusa0Eaid0EidUSBRE96E0ASC20A130A7150DfeedType0FRSS0GfeedName0FworldNews/story01.htm</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>Nigerian activists demand arrest of Sudan''s Bashir in court</title><link>http://feeds.reuters.com/~r/Reuters/worldNews/~3/XPiyU5-52kk/story01.htm</link><description>LAGOS (Reuters) - Nigerian activists filed a suit with the Federal High Court in Abuja on Monday demanding that Sudanese President Omar al-Bashir be arrested and handed over to the International Criminal Court, which is seeking him on an international arrest warrant.&lt;img width=''1'' height=''1'' src=''http://reuters.us.feedsportal.com/c/35217/f/654198/s/2eb13a8e/mf.gif'' border=''0''/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/165666625156/u/49/f/654198/c/35217/s/2eb13a8e/a2.htm"&gt;&lt;img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/165666625156/u/49/f/654198/c/35217/s/2eb13a8e/a2.img" border="0"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;img width="1" height="1" src="http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/165666625156/u/49/f/654198/c/35217/s/2eb13a8e/a2t.img" border="0"/&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;\r\n&lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=XPiyU5-52kk:SuSkLwosYYA:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=XPiyU5-52kk:SuSkLwosYYA:F7zBnMyn0Lo"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?i=XPiyU5-52kk:SuSkLwosYYA:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=XPiyU5-52kk: