eapons</title><link>http://feeds.reuters.com/~r/Reuters/worldNews/~3/iUuFfD7wU_U/story01.htm</link><description>PANAMA CITY (Reuters) - Panama has detained a North Korean-flagged ship coming from Cuba as it approached the Panama Canal with undeclared weapons, President Ricardo Martinelli said.&lt;img width=''1'' height=''1'' src=''http://reuters.us.feedsportal.com/c/35217/f/654198/s/2eb62717/mf.gif'' border=''0''/&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;\r\n&lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=iUuFfD7wU_U:LQfC_qckt_o:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=iUuFfD7wU_U:LQfC_qckt_o:F7zBnMyn0Lo"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?i=iUuFfD7wU_U:LQfC_qckt_o:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=iUuFfD7wU_U:LQfC_qckt_o:V_sGLiPBpWU"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?i=iUuFfD7wU_U:LQfC_qckt_o:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Reuters/worldNews/~4/iUuFfD7wU_U" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><category domain="">worldNews</category><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2013 06:20:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/07/16/us-panama-northkorea-idUSBRE96F08420130716?feedType=RSS&amp;feedName=worldNews</guid><feedburner:origLink>http://reuters.us.feedsportal.com/c/35217/f/654198/s/2eb62717/l/0L0Sreuters0N0Carticle0C20A130C0A70C160Cus0Epanama0Enorthkorea0EidUSBRE96F0A8420A130A7160DfeedType0FRSS0GfeedName0FworldNews/story01.htm</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>New North Korea curbs endanger aid efforts: relief worker</title><link>http://feeds.reuters.com/~r/Reuters/worldNews/~3/u2c1PCDDl_Q/story01.htm</link><description>BEIJING (Reuters) - New sanctions levied on North K