7/f/654198/s/2ebc01b5/l/0L0Sreuters0N0Carticle0C20A130C0A70C160Cus0Eyemen0Enetherlands0Ekidnap0EidUSBRE96F0AM620A130A7160DfeedType0FRSS0GfeedName0FworldNews/story01.htm</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>Former Japan premier sues PM Abe for libel over Fukushima comments</title><link>http://feeds.reuters.com/~r/Reuters/worldNews/~3/j2kV5H9FZF8/story01.htm</link><description>TOKYO (Reuters) - Japan''s prime minister at the time of the 2011 Fukushima nuclear disaster said on Tuesday he would sue the current premier, Shinzo Abe, for defamation over an article criticizing the emergency operation he supervised during the crisis.&lt;img width=''1'' height=''1'' src=''http://reuters.us.feedsportal.com/c/35217/f/654198/s/2ebb61c4/mf.gif'' border=''0''/&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;\r\n&lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=j2kV5H9FZF8:DvVG1_eiOUc:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=j2kV5H9FZF8:DvVG1_eiOUc:F7zBnMyn0Lo"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?i=j2kV5H9FZF8:DvVG1_eiOUc:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.reuters.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?a=j2kV5H9FZF8:DvVG1_eiOUc:V_sGLiPBpWU"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Reuters/worldNews?i=j2kV5H9FZF8:DvVG1_eiOUc:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Reuters/worldNews/~4/j2kV5H9FZF8" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><category domain="">worldNews</category><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2013 12:18:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/07/16/us-japan-prime-minister-lawsuit-idUSBRE96F0K220130716?feedType=RSS&amp;feedName=worldNews</guid><feedburner:origLink>http://reuters.us.feedsportal.com/c/35217/f/654198/s/2ebb61c4/l/0L0Sreuters0N0Carticle0C20A130C0A70C160