ow-about-royal-baby/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_europe/~3/AD8J42keyjk/index.html</link><description>Think you know all you could ever want to about royal babies amid all the excitement about the new arrival? Well did you know this...&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_europe/~4/AD8J42keyjk" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2013 10:44:01 EDT</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://edition.cnn.com/2013/07/16/world/europe/five-things-to-know-about-royal-baby/index.html</feedburner:origLink></item>\r\n<item><title>''Action man'' Putin in latest stunt</title><guid isPermaLink="false">http://edition.cnn.com/2013/07/16/world/action-man-russian-president-putin/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_europe/~3/_V8ELbxpyt8/index.html</link><description>He''s fired darts at a gray whale, sped through St Petersburg in an F1 car, and taken a supersonic flight in a bomber jet.&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_europe/~4/_V8ELbxpyt8" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2013 10:24:44 EDT</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://edition.cnn.com/2013/07/16/world/action-man-russian-president-putin/index.html</feedburner:origLink></item>\r\n<item><title>How air pollution kills millions</title><guid isPermaLink="false">http://edition.cnn.com/2013/07/16/world/air-pollution-killing-study/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_europe/~3/cVMk5B_V2wk/index.html</link><description>More than two million people are dying every year from the effects of outdoor air pollution, according to a new study. Half of those premature deaths took place in East Asia thanks to soaring air pollution levels.&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_europe/~4/cVMk5B_V2wk" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2013 08:16:13 EDT</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://edition.cnn.com/2013/07/16/world/air-pollution-killing-study/index.