erican wanted by Italy in rendition case arrested in Panama</title><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/18/world/americas/panama-italy-us-rendition/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_world/~3/BOilFKSlNUU/index.html</link><description>One of the 23 Americans whom an Italian court convicted in absentia of kidnapping a terrorism suspect in 2003 has been arrested in Panama on an Italian arrest warrant, the Italian justice ministry''s press office said Thursday.&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_world/~4/BOilFKSlNUU" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2013 07:38:38 EDT</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/18/world/americas/panama-italy-us-rendition/index.html</feedburner:origLink></item>\r\n<item><title>81 kidnapped migrants rescued in Mexico</title><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/18/world/americas/mexico-migrants-rescued/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_world/~3/4o704UPTcls/index.html</link><description>A group of 81 migrants held captive in a house in the border city of Reynosa were rescued by Mexican authorities.&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/edition_world/~4/4o704UPTcls" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2013 07:38:46 EDT</pubDate><feedburner:origLink>http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/18/world/americas/mexico-migrants-rescued/index.html</feedburner:origLink></item>\r\n<item><title>Taliban to Malala: Why we shot you</title><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/17/world/asia/pakistan-taliban-malala/index.html</guid><link>http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_world/~3/610otsqzRQQ/index.html</link><description>In a letter to a Pakistani schoolgirl shot in the head on her way home from school, a senior Taliban commander purportedly tells her that she was targeted not because she advocated education for all girls, but rather for her criticism of the militant group.&lt;img src="htt